    "description": "行驶中车内日常对话池。speaker: taoxia/linli; response 可选。"
  },
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "CHAT_001",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "路上好安静啊……以前这条路上还能碰到流浪商队的。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "现在只剩我们了。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_002",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你说，温室社区的番茄罐头为什么那么受欢迎？明明味道一般啊。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_003",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……油压表刚才跳了一下。可能是路面震动，先记一下。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_004",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "嘿嘿，我刚才在货箱里发现一块旧巧克力包装纸。闻起来还有一点点甜味呢。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "别乱翻货物啊。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_005",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "这段路的路基还算结实。以前应该是省道。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["main_road", "highway"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_006",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "总觉得废墟游民营地的人看我们的眼神怪怪的……不过至少生意做得成。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_007",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "林砾，你有没有想过以后不跑商了做什么？",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "没想过。车能跑就继续跑。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_008",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……天色不太好。希望不是辐射云。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "hazard"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_009",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "出发啦！今天的货应该挺好卖的。",
      "weight": 60,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 0.15],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_010",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "快到了吧？我已经开始想象卸完货之后吃什么了。",
      "weight": 55,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.8, 1.0],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "先把货交了再说。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_011",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "轮胎磨损比预期快了一点……下次该换备件了。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.4, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_012",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你知道吗，钟楼那边有个老爷爷，收集了整整一墙的旧唱片。下次去了我想再听听。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_013",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "陶夏，别把脚搁在仪表台上。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "好嘛好嘛~",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1, "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_014",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "这条路两边都是旧楼，感觉随时会塌下来……开快点吧？",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "hazard"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_015",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "哇，刚才路过的那片废墟好大……以前是个商场吗？",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_016",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "走一半了。油耗正常。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.45, 0.55],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_017",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "林砾你困不困？要不要我讲个笑话？……算了我讲的笑话你从来不笑。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "讲吧。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_018",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "到站前把送货单再对一遍。别又搞错了。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.85, 1.0],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_019",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你有没有觉得……每次离开一个地方，再回来的时候它都变了一点点？",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "人也是。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_020",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "后视镜松了。下次停车我紧一下。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.1, 0.5],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_021",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "如果旧时代的人看到我们现在这样子，会怎么想？一辆破卡车装着半车罐头到处跑。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_022",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……嗯？没事。刚走神了。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.4, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "想什么呢？",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_023",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "我以前在钟楼看到过一本旧相册。里面的人笑得好开心，去海边度假什么的。那个叫'旅游'吧？",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 11,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_024",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "肚子有点饿了……还有多久到啊？",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.5, 0.85],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "忍忍。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_025",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "这条小路比上次来的时候宽了一点。有人在维护。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["path"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_026",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "我在副驾发现了一颗螺丝。不知道是从哪掉下来的……要紧吗？",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "给我看看。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_027",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "速度保持在四十左右。这个路况不能更快了。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "path"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_028",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你说，如果有天所有路都修好了，世界是不是就算恢复正常了？",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": ["main_road"],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "也许吧。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_029",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "下次路过温室的时候，帮我带一株薄荷苗回来好不好？我想种在车里。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "车里种不活。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_030",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……前面有段下坡。坐稳了。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_001",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "沈禾说他们今年种的番茄比去年甜。我试了一口——确实！不知道是不是水质变好了。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_002",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……温室到废墟这条路，我已经能闭着眼开了。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch1_done"],
      "response": {
        "text": "那你闭着眼开试试？",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1, "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_003",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "伍拾七那家伙，看着凶巴巴的，其实每次我们走的时候都会多塞两个净水片。嘴硬心软。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ruins_market_intro"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "response": {
        "text": "……他只是不想我们饿死在路上丢他面子。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_004",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "刀鱼今天又想卖给我一个'旧时代珍品'。这次是一个发光的方盒子。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ruins_market_intro"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "response": {
        "text": "……那是电池充电器。问她多少钱。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_005",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……赵苗说外围农场的灌溉渠堵了一段。下趟可以帮她带根管子。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch1_done"],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_006",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "麻薯今天跑得好稳！你是不是调过悬挂了？",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……昨天调的。减震弹簧换了。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_007",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……收音机刚才收到一段杂音。大概是干扰。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch1_done"],
      "response": {
        "text": "是吗？我还以为是一首歌呢。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_008",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "老甘的夜市烤肉真的好好吃……虽然不知道是什么肉。不不不，我不要知道。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ruins_market_intro"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……别问了。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_009",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你有没有觉得……我们跑的路线越来越远了？",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.8],
      "required_flags": ["sd_ch1_03_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch1_done"],
      "response": {
        "text": "远单利润高。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_010",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……这段路旁边的花开了。以前没注意过。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.7],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    }
  ]
